<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    {{ include head }}
    <title> CSIT </title>
</head>

<body>

    <section id="main">
        <video src="{{ get_asset bg.mp4 }}" muted autoplay loop></video>
        <div id="header">
            {{ include header }}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="homepage--banner top">
        <div class="head" id="head">Chemical Society of IISER Thiruvananthapuram (CSIT)</div>
        <div class="description">We are a group of chemistry enthusiasts who seek to learn and share knowledge about
            anything relating to the chemical world with the wider student fraternity, and also have fun in the process.
            We organize several events towards this end, including but not limited to competitions, talks, workshops and
            seminars. We also have an active social media presence, where we share informative and fun content.</div>
    </section>

    <section class="carousel--container">
        <div id="carousel">

            <section class="game-section">
                <h2 class="line-title">Snapshots</h2>
                <div class="owl-carousel custom-carousel owl-theme">

                    <div class="item active"
                        style="background-image: url('https://i.postimg.cc/q7q0pBRH/The-Catalyst.png');">
                        <div class="item-desc">
                            <h3>The Catalyst</h3>
                            <p>
                                <br>
                            <div class="date">29t March 2024</div>
                           This edition explores the unconventional phenomena of attraction between like charges in silica microparticles. Our newsletter also focuses on the latest research on nanoparticles and how it can be used to make a self-cleaning wall paint and in making tunable green catalysts.
                            <br> <br> <a href="#text">Read more</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="item"
                        style="background-image: url(https://i.postimg.cc/fTDGwW2q/synthesis2.jpg);">
                        <div class="item-desc">
                            <h3>Synthesis</h3>
                            <p>
                                <br>
                            Synthesis is back with it's newest edition.
This edition features articles honoring the name 'Synthesis' and delves into diverse topics such as computational studies, molecular electronics, and more!
                            <br> <br> <a href="{{ get_link magazine }}">Read more</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    </div>
    </section>


